            "description": "Creates a new user account. No authentication required.\n\n`userType` can be `admin`, `barber`, or `user` (default: `user`).\n\n`document` must be a valid CPF — validated with the full digit verifier algorithm. Accepted formats: `123.456.789-09` or `12345678909`."
          }
